metadata.name: GSU Early Pass
metadata.description:
Take ownership!  
Become a part of the GSU community and help us spread the values and message of shared Stability, Efficiency, Equality and Prosperity for all.

As an Early Pass holder, you will get access to gated communication channels with like-minded people, contributing to a pool of knowledge from diverse areas of expertise and backgrounds. You will also be granted early access to our future NFT drops and other releases with our partners and collaborators.

We recommend you to hold tight to your Pass. 
We have great ideas and considerations for you going forward!
